AI 분석 패널 (탭 전환 아래에, 기존 mode 탭 UI는 `{!analyzeMode && (...)}` 로 감싸기):
```jsx
{analyzeMode && (
  <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 16 }}>
    <label style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', gap: 12, border: '2px dashed #CBD5E1', borderRadius: 20, padding: 32, cursor: 'pointer', background: BG }}>
